name: FTemplateSequenceBindingOverrideData
doc:
Template sequence binding override data

This is similar to FMovieSceneBindingOverrideData, but works only for a template sequence's root object,
so we don't need it to store the object binding ID.

Object: Specifies the object binding to override.
bOverridesDefault: Specifies whether the default assignment should remain bound (false) or if this should completely override the default binding (true).
